      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To provide that Members of Congress shall be paid last whenever the Treasury is unable to satisfy the obligations of the United States Government in a timely manner because the public debt limit has been reached.</title>
      </item>
